      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CLAYMORE LASS (3) hit the ground running from an outside draw with a fast early split, holding on for a minor placing when third and beaten 5 lengths at this track over 530m in 30.88. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Capable of going well again. WILMA'S OUR GIRL (1) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (30.61) from Box 1 at this track. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Can feature again. VICTA WALLY (2) has been in super consistent form recently with two minors on end before breaking through for an overdue win (30.77) at this track. Performs well off this draw. Best form too dangerous to ignore. Have to include. BIG STRETCH (8) will have admirers after placing last time out.",
